# Standup Generator

AI-powered standup report generator for Slack and Teams, pulling data from Jira.

## Structure

```
apps/slack/     # Slack bot (Next.js + Bolt)
apps/teams/     # Teams bot (Next.js + Bot Framework)
packages/core/  # Shared library (@standup/core)
```

## Commands

```bash
npm run dev     # Start all apps (Slack:3001, Teams:3002)
npm run build   # Build all packages
npm run lint    # Lint all packages
```

